{
  "id": "RAW_3e31b9e7",
  "title": "智能体基础设施 - Vercel",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/agentic-infrastructure",
  "date": "2026-04-09 21:32:02",
  "author": "Tom Occhino",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__XJFYTq__content\">\n   <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-between flex-initial w-full gap-4 pt-2\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-1.5 flex-initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">4<!-- --> min <!-- -->read</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6 flex-1 justify-start\"></div>\n    <time class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 order-2 md:order-3\" datetime=\"2026-04-09T00:00-07:00\">Apr 9, 2026</time>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Every generation of software eventually demands a new generation of infrastructure.</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">First, we configured servers by hand.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Next, the cloud turned infrastructure into APIs.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Then, a more important shift: <a target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/blog/framework-defined-infrastructure\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\" href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/framework-defined-infrastructure\">infrastructure derived from the application itself.</a></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">LLMs and coding agents are driving the next transition, and it's happening fast.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">In just three months, weekly deployments on Vercel have doubled, and agents are driving the growth. Today, over 30% of deployments are initiated by coding agents, up 1000% from six months ago. Claude Code accounts for 75%, Lovable and <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono);font-feature-settings:&quot;tnum&quot;\">v0</span> for 6%, and Cursor for 1.5%.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#software-is-now-agentic\" id=\"software-is-now-agentic\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Software is now agentic</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Agents are building, testing, and shipping AI-native software, and they're doing it at a velocity that breaks traditional operations. Vercel projects deployed by coding agents are 20 times more likely to call AI inference providers than those deployed by humans. Agents are writing software that uses AI, and agents are building agents.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">As the final actor shifts from human to machine, infrastructure has to adapt again. It has to work for software that acts on behalf of users, writes itself, and increasingly needs to understand its own behavior in production. This new generation of agentic software demands <b>Agentic Infrastructure</b>.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">It’s not one evolution, but three:</p>\n   <ol class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__orderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Infrastructure for coding agents to deploy to</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Infrastructure for building and running agents</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Infrastructure that itself is agentic</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 max-w-none not-frist:mt-20 not-first:mb-10 mx-0 max-[600px]:max-w-none max-[600px]:px-7 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pr-14 max-[600px]:[li_&amp;]:pl-0 max-[600px]:w-full max-[600px]:mt-12 max-[600px]:mb-6\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"334\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__V2UKpG__desktop rounded-md image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40yq8xRZTa8PQNd14FjmBI%2F71fd0bde4688ebb0fba0ea6062dd2824%2Fagentic-infra-light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40yq8xRZTa8PQNd14FjmBI%2F71fd0bde4688ebb0fba0ea6062dd2824%2Fagentic-infra-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40yq8xRZTa8PQNd14FjmBI%2F71fd0bde4688ebb0fba0ea6062dd2824%2Fagentic-infra-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"789\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic blog-mobile-and-mode-dependent-media-module__V2UKpG__mobile image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7iAatv8lmCz0gWWzGRNpaP%2F2ab3b17c01516dd8240ec4f438d53498%2Fagentic-infra-m-light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7iAatv8lmCz0gWWzGRNpaP%2F2ab3b17c01516dd8240ec4f438d53498%2Fagentic-infra-m-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F7iAatv8lmCz0gWWzGRNpaP%2F2ab3b17c01516dd8240ec4f438d53498%2Fagentic-infra-m-light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#1.-infrastructure-for-coding-agents-to-deploy-to\" id=\"1.-infrastructure-for-coding-agents-to-deploy-to\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>1. Infrastructure for coding agents to deploy to</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">The bottleneck for agentic engineering is operational friction.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">When a coding agent writes a feature, it requires a place to run, test, and verify the output, which ultimately means it needs a URL. If the path from code to running system involves manual Terraform state or clicks in a cloud console UI, the autonomous loop breaks. Agents need programmatic, deterministic deployment surfaces.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">This is why <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/deployments\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/deployments\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">immutable deployments</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/deployments/generated-urls\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/deployments/generated-urls\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">preview URLs</a> on every commit, and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/instant-rollback\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/instant-rollback\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">instant rollbacks</a> aren't just developer experience upgrades anymore. They are absolute prerequisites for machine-driven software development.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Vercel's <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/cli\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/cli\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">CLI</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/rest-api\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/rest-api\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">API</a>, <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/agent-resources/vercel-mcp\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/agent-resources/vercel-mcp\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">MCP servers</a>, and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/git\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/git\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">git integration</a> give agents native access to a deployment surface where they can generate code, open a PR, get a preview URL, verify the output, and ship to production, all without human intervention.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#2.-infrastructure-for-building-and-running-agents\" id=\"2.-infrastructure-for-building-and-running-agents\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>2. Infrastructure for building and running agents</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Serverless workloads need functions, caching, and short-lived requests at the edge, but managing that stack yourself means config drift and hours debugging across systems. Vercel solved that by unifying every layer into the frontend cloud.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Agent workloads are a fundamentally different shape. They require long-lived execution, multi-step orchestration, model routing, cost controls, sandboxed code execution, and abuse resistance. It's a more complex stack, and the penalty for running it yourself compounds: every wasted request burns inference dollars, provider outages take your agent offline, and untrusted code opens the door to prompt injection.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Vercel's agentic infrastructure unifies every AI primitive we've built into a single, secure platform, the same way we did for serverless.</p>\n   <ul class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__unorderedList\">\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-sdk\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-sdk\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>AI SDK</b></a> gives developers a unified way to build AI-powered applications across frameworks and providers, and <a target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/blog/ai-sdk-6\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\" href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/ai-sdk-6\">AI SDK 6</a> adds an agent abstraction so developers can define an agent once and reuse it across interfaces and workflows.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Chat SDK</b></a> makes agents available across dozens of chat apps and platforms from a single codebase.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>AI Gateway</b></a> gives teams a single endpoint for hundreds of models, with budgets, monitoring, routing, retries, and fallbacks.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/fluid-compute\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/fluid-compute\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Fluid compute</b></a> is designed for the unusual shape of AI workloads, where latency, concurrency, and idle waiting all matter at once.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/workflow\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/workflow\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Workflows</b></a><b> </b>and<b> </b><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/queues\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/queues\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Queues</b></a> give agents a way to pause, resume, retry, maintain state, and offload background work.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/sandbox\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/sandbox\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Sandbox</b></a> gives them isolated execution environments for untrusted code.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph text-module__qZtYrq__listItem\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/observability\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/observability\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\"><b>Observability</b></a> lets teams trace what agents are doing and where they are going wrong.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Together, these building blocks give developers everything they need to build and run agents in one place. But Vercel also puts each of them into a single system with shared context: code, model calls, and runtime behavior. That context is what turns the infrastructure itself into an agent.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#3.-infrastructure-that-is-itself-agentic\" id=\"3.-infrastructure-that-is-itself-agentic\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>3. Infrastructure that is itself agentic</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Traditional infrastructure is a one-way street: code goes in, logs come out, and a human reads the logs to fix the code. A unified platform provides complete visibility across every layer in real time, giving agents the ability to not just monitor production, but autonomously respond to it.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">When a latency spike hits a critical route or a model provider drops requests, Vercel doesn't wait for a human to notice. It investigates the anomaly, queries observability data, reads logs, inspects source code, performs root-cause analysis, and reviews proposed fixes in isolated sandboxes. The platform interprets what the developer intended, observes what the system actually did, and acts on the delta.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Today, that still happens with human approval in the loop. Over time, the platform will take on more of that operational burden, not because it's replacing developers, but because it has enough context to act on their behalf.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text-heading-24 md:text-heading-32 font-semibold pt-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:pt-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;:first-child]:pt-0 w-full group relative text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-[calc(var(--grid-divider-gap)/1.5)] [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#where-we're-going\" id=\"where-we're-going\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Where we're going</h2>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">The history of cloud computing is the history of removing the human from the machine. Agentic infrastructure is the next evolution, moving us from passive tools that wait for commands to proactive systems that act on our behalf.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">The companies that win the next decade will build on infrastructure that expects software to write, ship, and heal itself.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 将“智能体基础设施”定义为云计算的下一次演进，旨在支持目前已驱动超过 30% 部署量的 AI 智能体快速增长。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 将“智能体基础设施”定义为云计算的下一次演进，旨在支持目前已驱动超过 30% 部署量的 AI 智能体快速增长。",
  "summary": "Vercel 引入了“智能体基础设施”的概念，以应对从以人为中心向机器驱动的软件开发模式的转变。随着 Claude Code 和 Cursor 等编程智能体使部署速度翻倍，传统基础设施产生了操作摩擦。Vercel 的愿景包含三个支柱：为智能体提供程序化的部署界面；提供用于构建和运行智能体的统一技术栈（包括 AI SDK、沙盒和流式计算）；以及通过共享上下文使基础设施自身能够自主监控、诊断并修复生产环境问题。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "编程智能体正在从根本上改变部署模式和速度。",
      "explanation": "目前超过 30% 的 Vercel 部署由智能体发起，它们调用 AI 推理的可能性是人类驱动项目的 20 倍，这促使基础设施设计必须进行变革。"
    },
    {
